{"tid":1880873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輸乜撚野呀？用下個腦啦！","createTime":"2020-02-15T07:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T11:35:07.000Z","uid":294714,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf0a54cc667e90c02d0e26707faa7e538e229fb","tid":1880873,"uid":294714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:29:59.000Z","msg":"成鳩日話場疫情完左就輸<br />\n你無撚野呀？<br />\n由頭到尾講攬炒都係我哋攬住支那炒<br />\n唔佢班撚屌攬住我地炒呀<br />\n場疫情爆 唔單止佢地死 我地都死呀<br />\n咁仲光咩復香港呀？<br />\n想贏大撚把方法啦<br />\n黃色經濟圈 罷工 呢啲唔係方法？<br />\n問題係你地唔肯出全力去做呀<br />\n連有支那病毒都照返工<br />\n贏條撚呀？<br />\n用自己方法主動攬炒先叫贏<br />\n我地依家比支共夾硬攬埋一齊死<br />\n你地仲咁開心<br />\n無撚野呀？<br />\n認真諗下場運動仲有咩出路啦<br />\n日鳩日淨係諗點買口罩<br />\n坐係屋企等死<br />\n到時啲人死曬就當贏<br />\n你話隻病毒淨係傳比班狗同藍絲就話唔緊要<br />\n由得佢地死<br />\n屌你自己友都會中架<br />\n唔該你哋唔好再戇鳩鳩咁啦"},{"pid":"520348d303cd3c9e80ccb16226e1cd91be2dee9e","tid":1880873,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"林鄭做返啱...我地就輸....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1023c82e2ec7716330abd1f1692c2cf169350810","tid":1880873,"uid":6777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"520348d303cd3c9e80ccb16226e1cd91be2dee9e","tid":1880873,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"林鄭做返啱...我地就輸....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"咁撤回果陣咪已經輸撚左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c987e711e768158c47e3b73d9e1399283e34d64","tid":1880873,"uid":294714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"520348d303cd3c9e80ccb16226e1cd91be2dee9e","tid":1880873,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislik